# db/seeds — reference seed data + dev fixtures.
#
# EndorseKit's one substantial seed asset is the AC 61-65 endorsement
# template catalog: the canonical list of instructor endorsements
# (solo, solo cross-country, knowledge test, practical test, flight
# review, IPC, etc.), each with its AC 61-65 paragraph reference, its
# regulatory citation, and a parameterized text template. This catalog
# is transcribed once from the current AC 61-65 revision and checked in
# here as YAML, then loaded by the Phase 5 seed loader. See
# docs/product-research.md §4.4.
#
# This file is a placeholder so the empty directory is tracked by git.
